data.text:
All My Children cast list, including photos of the actors when available. This list includes all of the All My Children main actors and actresses, so if they are an integral part of the show you'll find them below. You can various bits of trivia about these All My Children stars, such as where the actor was born and what their year of birth is. This cast list of actors from All My Children focuses primarily on the main characters, but there may be a few actors who played smaller roles on All My Children that are on here as well.

This poll contains items like Michelle Trachtenberg and Amanda Seyfried

If you are wondering, "Who are the actors from All My Children?" or "Who starred on All My Children?" then this list will help you answer those questions.

In most cases you can click on the names of these popular All My Children actors and actresses to find out more information about them. If you're looking for a particular All My Children actor or actress, then type their name into the "search" bar to find them directly.
